Package pl.put.poznan.BuildingInfo.logic

Class Room

java.lang.Object
pl.put.poznan.BuildingInfo.logic.Location
pl.put.poznan.BuildingInfo.logic.Room
public class Room extends Location
Represents a room within a building. This class extends the abstract class Location and provides specific functionality for managing properties and calculations related to a room.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Paulina Guzior, Jakub Binkowski, Benedykt Huszcza, Jan Wybieralski

  • Constructor Details

    • Room

      public Room(int id, String name, double area, double cube, float heating, int light)
      Constructs a new Room with the specified identifier, name, area, cube, heating, and light.
      Parameters:
      id - The unique identifier of the room.
      name - The name of the room.
      area - The area of the room in square meters.
      cube - The volume (cube) of the room in cubic meters.
      heating - The heating level of the room.
      light - The light intensity of the room.
